{"tid":721712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子懾車罅過路 遭紅Van撞低","createTime":"2018-06-29T01:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T01:03:30.000Z","uid":122,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"541b65d2867396914e4d06f439643c4246574085","tid":721712,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T01:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180629/large/1530228448_3421.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180629%2Flarge%2F1530228448_3421.jpg&h=82700086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n筲箕灣道157號對開東行線巴士站，早上6時26分，巴士埋站期間，一名男子從車罅之間橫過馬路，一輛紅頂小巴駛至，司機煞車不及，將過路男子撞倒，幸仍然清醒，事後送院治理。小巴司機協助調查。"}]}